// XA
NOTE READ ORDER
GRAB 300
MARK READ_ORDER
  COPY F M
  ADDI X 1 X
  TEST X < 5
  TJMP READ_ORDER

NOTE HALT = DROP + HALT
HALT


// XB
NOTE APPEND ORDER
LINK 800

GRAB 200
SEEK 9999
MARK APPEND_ORDER
  COPY M F
  ADDI X 1 X
  TEST X < 5
  TJMP APPEND_ORDER

NOTE HALT = DROP + HALT
HALT